relation: Darrow - #49 The greatest dance off of all time begins. Will Captain Strong's pose of extreme beauty beat the awesome power of Ness' PK Break Dancin'?!

Darrow - #50 With great power...comes great backpain. Captain Strong shows his age and the battle comes to an end. Ness, content with his victory, proceeds onto Twoson and the chapter of Onett comes to a close. Also, a cameo by yours truly as the mysterious Check-a-roony guy.
Darrow - #51 Ness travels on his way into Twoson and picks up a new friend in the process: Reginald Jr, the exit mouse.
Darrow - #52 An important call makes its way to Ness in his sleep. Also, exit mouse has both a gambling addiction and a side job of selling faulty rulers.
Darrow - #53 A bike shop that holds...you guessed it, mohawks. Unfortunately, bike riding lessons were not included.
